{"type":"text","timestamp":1779249540475,"sessionID":"ses_1bc8c0c0bffeEZb75VgBylzEVF","part":{"id":"prt_e4389357c001uYMUnjjdQZMYlz","messageID":"msg_e43892614001nHugJPtgq3GYya","sessionID":"ses_1bc8c0c0bffeEZb75VgBylzEVF","type":"text","text":"Inquiries module implementation complete. Here's a summary:\n\n**Files created (5):**\n- `inquiry.repository.ts` — `BaseRepository<Inquiry>` with `findByUser()` and `findByFilters()` (QueryBuilder with status/propertyId/search filtering)\n- `dto/submit-inquiry.dto.ts` — validates message (10-2000 chars), optional name/email/phone overrides\n- `dto/respond-inquiry.dto.ts` — validates response (10-5000 chars)\n- `dto/index.ts` — barrel export\n- `inquiry-submit.controller.ts` — handles nested `POST /api/properties/:propertyId/inquiries` (renter-only)\n\n**Files modified (3):**\n- `inquiry.service.ts` — rewritten to extend `BaseService<Inquiry>`, adds `submitInquiry` (denormalization), `listInquiries` (filters/search), `markAsRead`, `respondToInquiry`, and `user`→`renter` response mapping\n- `inquiry.controller.ts` — rewritten with `@UseGuards(RolesGuard)`, `@Roles` per-endpoint, Swagger decorators, proper response envelopes, self-healed `GET /inquiries/my`\n- `inquiry.module.ts` — registers `InquiryRepository`, imports `Property`+`User` entities, adds `InquirySubmitController`\n\n**Endpoints (7):**\n| POST `/api/properties/:id/inquiries` | GET `/api/inquiries` | GET `/api/inquiries/my` | GET `/api/inquiries/:id` | PATCH `/api/inquiries/:id/read` | POST `/api/inquiries/:id/respond` | DELETE `/api/inquiries/:id` |\n\n**Verification:** `npx tsc --noEmit` passes with zero errors. Report written to `.claude-project/nestfind/status/BACKEND_IMPLEMENT_inquiries.md`.","time":{"start":1779249526140,"end":1779249540471}}}
